messages.message: Hi France, hope to establish communication lines with you as early as possible! What are your thoughts on Belgium?

Hi England, what are your thoughts on Belgium?

I'd like to have a strong alliance between the two of us!
Hi Russia, can I ask what your plans are for Warsaw?

I'd definitely be open to seeing a French Belgium as long as we're working together.

Would you be willing to move Kiel to Holland?
Hi Italy, can we agree that Tyrolia should be a DMZ?
Hey Germany! Any chance you would consider moving to Silesia this first turn? I'd be happy to help out if you are.
I'd rather not. Can we agree to keep Tyrolia, Bohemia and Silesia as a DMZ? I think we are the two nations that stand the most to gain from working together.
Agreed!
Kiel is moving to Denmark, I prefer to open that way as Germany.
I'm happy to work together! Have you heard from anyone else?
Austria and I can agree to this?

I understand the opening to Denmark. I'd still prefer to see the fleet in Holland since you can't take Denmark and Holland in the same move, but you wouldn't be able to take Holland in the same move. You'd be able to support me into Belgium while moving to Denmark in the fall.

You'd be giving Russia Sweden in the process. That's a win-win in my eyes.
Perfect! We should work together against Russia if he proves antagonistic. Have you heard from anyone else?
I'm sure England will try for Belgium and I don't want that happening. Have you heard from anyone else?
Just France and you.
This is a press game, I'm not going to let Russia gain Sweden.
I'd appreciate an answer.

No one has except you and Austria.

I'm trying to get Russia to move north, it'd keep England from gaining too much strength. Do you think you'd be able to move strongly against Russia?
What about Italy?
Still waiting to hear from him.
I'd need to be able to do so without leaving myself open to a stab from the south. Are you and England agreeing not to enter the channel?
Have you heard anything from him?
He hasn't answered me either.

England hasn't messaged me yet. But he hasn't messaged me at all. I assume he's doing the same with everyone else.

You and I should work together regardless.

Would you be willing to DMZ Burgundy and Ruhr if I move into the channel?

Munich -> Silesia -> Warsaw works well if you get a DMZ from Austria.
Agreed.
Same here.
Has England messaged you at all?
And France says he wants you to move against England. Sounds like it could be a Western Triple?
If you can open strongly against Russia, I'll open heavily against England. We can work together to eliminate both of them.
That's what it sounds like so far. But England has said nothing to me. I prefer to stick with strong communicative allies. It's just as beneficial for both of us!
Have you been able to DMZ Galicia with Russia?

Hi England, what are your plans for the opening?

I've been hearing some concerning news regarding you and France working together against me. I'd appreciate an answer to my messages.
